Metadata: University of California Sea Grant Extension Program

Tidelines will be published quarterly as a local newsletter dealing with practical problems in the areas of Commercial and sport fisheries; Seafood processing, aquaculture, marine education and youth programs, marine research, waterfront management, boating industry, marine transportation, environmental policy, and coastal engineering. Cover article: Severe weather planning for marinas, boatyards and yacht clubs, Public meetings: Pacific Fishery Management Council, Coast Guard severe weather tips for boaters and dock owners, New California Sea Grant logo.
